summary: A small cabin in The Rift, located in a river
descriptionHtml:
[b]This is an update to my first ever house mod, when criticizing please keep that I am new to this in mind.

[/b]Sorry for my english.

No DLCs are required! ApachiiSkyHair is only required if you care about the body at the back of the house having hair, but you should get it anyway, it is a good mod.


This mod adds one new house located in The Rift, it is fully navmeshed, features crafting stations (In the basement), named storages, and a bed, it is a simple starter house with plenty of custom models, nothing too fancy, it is fairly small cozy home, the style it uses fits in with the lore a fair amount, I find the location unique enough, what more could you possibly want?

And the answer to that is likely naked women BUT I will not add those.

That is all, I would like feedback, feel free to request new things.
author: Egonblade
